## Code Patterns to Reference

### Filter Pattern (Client-side via TanStack DB)
```typescript
const libraryQuery = useLiveQuery((q) =>
  q.from({ item: libraryCollection })
    .where(item => {
      if (filters.type !== 'all') {
        return item.content.contentType === filters.type;
      }
      return true;
    })
    .orderBy(/* sort */)
);
```

### URL State Pattern
```typescript
// Update URL params
const params = new URLSearchParams($page.url.searchParams);
params.set('sort', sortBy);
params.set('page', '1');
goto(`?${params.toString()}`, { keepFocus: true });
```

### Server Load with Params
```typescript
export async function load({ url, locals }) {
  const page = parseInt(url.searchParams.get('page') ?? '1');
  const sortBy = url.searchParams.get('sort') ?? 'addedAt';
  const library = await api.access.getUserLibrary({ page, limit: 12, sortBy });
  return { library };
}
```

